title: These apps for your iPhone are better than the ones Apple makes
text:
embed 
Apple has dominated the smart phone industry for years, but that doesn't mean that all of its software is the best. There are quite a few applications that are better than the stock applications Apple loads onto your iPhone. Here are just a few apps that you should consider using instead.
